      • onTimesheet

        @RequestMapping(value="/timesheet",
                method=POST)
public java.lang.String onTimesheet(javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest request,
                                                                                                       @RequestParam(value="userId")
                                                                                                       java.lang.Integer userId,
                                                                                                       @RequestParam(value="oppId")
                                                                                                       java.lang.Integer oppId,
                                                                                                       @RequestParam(value="displayMonth")
                                                                                                       java.lang.Integer month,
                                                                                                       @RequestParam(value="displayYear")
                                                                                                       java.lang.Integer year,
                                                                                                       @RequestParam(value="newMonth")
                                                                                                       java.lang.Integer newMonth,
                                                                                                       @RequestParam(value="newYear")
                                                                                                       java.lang.Integer newYear,
                                                                                                       @RequestParam(value="timeData")
                                                                                                       java.lang.String timeData,
                                                                                                       @RequestParam(value="save")
                                                                                                       java.lang.Integer save,
                                                                                                       @RequestParam(value="dirty")
                                                                                                       java.lang.Integer dirty,
                                                                                                       org.springframework.web.bind.support.SessionStatus status,
                                                                                                       org.springframework.ui.Model model)
        Saves any changed time data to the database if it applies. Data not saved if unchanged or user elects not to save it. Time data formatted for display added to model in JSON format. message holds errors/success or "" if no data save required message class is css style for display
        Parameters:
        request -
        userId -
        oppId -
        month - this is the current month
        year - this is the current year
        newMonth - this is the updated month (previous/next)
        newYear - this is the updated year (previous/next)
        timeData - data to potentially be saved
        save - flag if user wants the data saved
        dirty - flag if data has changed
        status -
        model -
        Returns:
        timesheet.jsp model includes time data for month/year requested
